article.headline: Jefferson scores 22 in Little Rock's 85-60 victory over Tennessee State

images.name: Tennessee State Tigers vs. Little Rock : Game Highlights
images.caption: Tennessee State Tigers vs. Little Rock : Game Highlights

article.linkText: Jefferson scores 22 in Little Rock's 85-60 victory over Tennessee State
article.story: LITTLE ROCK, Ark. -- — Jordan Jefferson scored 22 points as Little Rock beat Tennessee State 85-60 on Thursday night. Jefferson added five rebounds for the Trojans (19-11, 13-4 Ohio Valley Conference). Bradley Douglas scored 19 points and added five rebounds and three steals. Deantoni Gordon was 7 of 12 shooting and 2 of 3 from the free throw line to finish with 16 points. The Trojans prolonged their winning streak to eight games. EJ Bellinger finished with 15 points for the Tigers (17-13, 10-7). Kinyon Hodges added 12 points and eight rebounds for Tennessee State. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
